Gain Insights on Data Directly at Source

The Sentiment Analysis template creates one recipe to perform the data analysis on the specified source object. To update the analysis data, you must schedule the recipe for your app.

To schedule the recipe, click the Recipes tab in Data Manager and select Schedule next to the recipe with the name of your app appended with Sentiment Analysis.

Select the time to run the recipe by minute, hour, week, or month. The recipe now runs at the scheduled day and time that you selected.
title: Scheduling Sentiment Analysis in Salesforce
